Package: steepcoind
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Steepcoin is a crypto-currency project forked from SteepCoin with aim to achieve
 energy-efficiency and keep as much as possible the original SteepCoin's
 preferable properties.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, steepcoind, and the CLI tool
 steepcoin-cli to interact with the daemon.

Package: steepcoin-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Steepcoin is a crypto-currency project forked from SteepCoin with aim to achieve
 energy-efficiency and keep as much as possible the original SteepCoin's
 preferable properties.
 .
 This package provides Steepcoin-Qt, a GUI client for Steepcoin based on Qt.

Package: steepcoin-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone transaction tool
 Steepcoin is a crypto-currency project forked from SteepCoin with aim to achieve
 energy-efficiency and keep as much as possible the original SteepCoin's
 preferable properties.
 This package provides steepcoin-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a steepcoin daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.
